ibis.cashmere.constellation

Interface InitLibraryFunction

  • Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface InitLibraryFunction
    Represents a method to initialize an OpenCL library. The OpenCL library can be initialized using the supplied cl_context and cl_command_queue.
